@MinioDotnet_HostAddress = http://localhost:5035

### Criar um Bucket
POST {{MinioDotnet_HostAddress}}/create-bucket
Content-Type: application/json

"meu-bucket"

### Listar Buckets
GET {{MinioDotnet_HostAddress}}/list-buckets

### Deletar um Bucket
DELETE {{MinioDotnet_HostAddress}}/delete-bucket/meu-bucket

### Upload de Arquivo
POST {{MinioDotnet_HostAddress}}/upload?bucketName=meu-bucket
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="teste.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

(Conteºdo do arquivo aqui)
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### Download de Arquivo
GET {{MinioDotnet_HostAddress}}/download/meu-bucket/teste.txt